Package pluto.models

Class AbstractModel

java.lang.Object
pluto.models.AbstractModel
Direct Known Subclasses:
CourseModel, SubjectModel, UserModel
public abstract class AbstractModel
extends java.lang.Object
Abstract model class in the MVC design pattern. Makes it possible for the the application to reach the database and manage the entities with the help of this class.
